---
// HourlyNote — single full-width line publishing the overage hourly.
// Lives as its own section so it's impossible to skim past.
---

<section class="bg-surface section-y">
  <div class="container-page">
    <div class="border-line bg-paper rounded-[var(--radius-card)] border p-7 md:flex md:items-baseline md:gap-6 md:p-9">
      <p class="text-accent font-serif text-3xl leading-none shrink-0">$95<span class="text-ink-soft text-lg">/hr</span></p>
      <p class="text-ink-soft mt-4 max-w-[52ch] text-[1.0625rem] leading-[1.6] md:mt-0 text-pretty">
        Bigger one-time changes outside your included monthly hour bill at
        <strong class="text-ink font-medium">$95 per hour, in 15-minute increments.</strong>
        You'll always get the estimate in writing before I start the timer.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
